linux-tools (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of linux-tools package.
  * Included 'rotn' script for Caesar cipher decryption.
  * Added manual page for 'rotn' under /usr/share/man/man1/.
  * Updated postinst script to create /opt/linux-tools directory and add it to PATH.

